OL,3,CFamily 'terrified' as couple held in
OL,4,CIran face verdict within days
OL,6,FA British couple detained in Iran,
OL,7,Fcharged with spying, could be handed a
OL,8,Fverdict within days, their family has
OL,9,Fsaid.
OL,11,FLindsay and Craig Foreman, from East
OL,12,FSussex, were taken into custody in
OL,13,FJanuary during a motorcycle tour
OL,14,Faround the world and were later
OL,15,Fcharged with espionage - accusations
OL,16,Fthe couple denies.
