OL,3,CFamily 'terrified' as couple held in
OL,4,CIran face verdict within days
OL,6,FThe couple appeared at a court in
OL,7,FTehran on Saturday, where they were
OL,8,Faccused and cross-examined in a trial
OL,9,Flasting less than three hours, the
OL,10,Ffamily said.
OL,12,FLindsay's son, Joe Bennett, said the
OL,13,Fcouple could be dealt a verdict and
OL,14,Fsentence within the next seven to ten
OL,15,Fdays.
OL,17,FHe said: "We are exhausted by the
OL,18,Funcertainty.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
