OL,3,CFamily 'terrified' as couple held in
OL,4,CIran face verdict within days
OL,6,F"I have nightmares thinking about how
OL,7,FMum and Craig can possibly be coping
OL,8,Fwith this injustice, hearing false
OL,9,Faccusations, feeling helpless to be
OL,10,Fable to defend themselves, knowing
OL,11,Fthat their words have been
OL,12,Fmistranslated.
OL,14,F"The court case may be moving forward,
OL,15,Fbut our parents are still trapped in
OL,16,Fhorrific conditions."
OL,18,FThe family previously said Lindsay was
OL,19,Fon a drip in prison, and Craig had
OL,20,Fseveral bouts of illness.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
