OL,3,CFamily 'terrified' as couple held in
OL,4,CIran face verdict within days
OL,6,F"Every day takes a toll and we are
OL,7,Fterrified by what may come next. This
OL,8,Fisn't justice, it's barely survival,"
OL,9,FJoe added.
OL,11,F"The UK Government must step in now
OL,12,Fand ensure Lindsay and Craig are not
OL,13,Fabandoned to an unfair process."
OL,15,FJoe described his parents' living
OL,16,Fconditions as unsanitary and cramped,
OL,17,Fadding that they are being forced to
OL,18,Fsleep on a metal bunk bed without a
OL,19,Fmattress, and continue to live with
OL,20,Funtreated illness.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
