OL,6,F"Every day that nothing happens
OL,7,Fcompounds their misery and pushes them
OL,8,Fcloser to the edge," he said.
OL,10,F"This is the nightmare that Craig and
OL,11,FLindsay cannot escape from and it is
OL,12,Fnow being compounded by unfair trial
OL,13,Fprocesses."
OL,15,FThe family said the judge has granted
OL,16,Fthe couple "limited welfare measures,"
OL,17,Fincluding an order for Craig to see a
OL,18,Fdentist, access to medicine, and
OL,19,Fpermission for basic items such as
OL,20,Fclothing and cooking utensils.
