OL,3,CFamily 'terrified' as couple held in
OL,4,CIran face verdict within days
OL,6,F"It should not take nine months and a
OL,7,Fcourt order to secure their basic
OL,8,Fwelfare," Joe said.
OL,10,FHe has since urged the Foreign,
OL,11,FCommonwealth and Development Office
OL,12,F(FCDO) to help secure the couple's
OL,13,Frelease.
OL,15,FForeign Secretary Yvette Cooper has
OL,16,Fagreed to meet with the family on
OL,17,FOctober 16, but Joe said action is
OL,18,Fneeded sooner.
OL,20,F"The UK Government cannot continue to
OL,21,Flet this just happen," he said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
